Name: Star Destroyer
About the game: You are a pilot of a spacecraft, your task is to destroy all enemies using various weapons. You need to move as far as possible into the depths of space. Collect elements from defeated enemies, they will restore your life. Classic arcade, space sroll. Nice graphics, several types of weapons. Control is done with the WASD buttons.
